<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: mathematical_context_schema  Entity: membership_of_maths_space_context  
   <express_ref linkend="mathematical_context_schema::mathematical_context_schema.membership_of_maths_space_context"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="mathematical_context_schema.membership_of_maths_space_context">
A membership_of_maths_space_context is an association between a maths_value_context and a maths_space_context that indicates the maths_value_context is a member of the maths_space_context.</ext_description>
